{"tid":2068624,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"20062020 Keep on Believing","createTime":"2020-06-17T23:02:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T04:34:13.000Z","uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"16fc2e0ada2b5d1d1e62438a8d411ae4d91dbcc2","tid":2068624,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T23:02:12.000Z","msg":"2020年6月18日 星期四 28-32℃<br />\n<br />\n部分時間有陽光，局部地區有驟雨。南至西南風3至4級。相對濕度70-90%。<br />\n<br />\n早晨，香港。<br />\n<br />\n清晨點唱：手紙 Angela Aki<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=siQJhIp-UTU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DsiQJhIp-UTU&d=u0uYB5UElWTGJsHKTdw4wfYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=52ca4247\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=siQJhIp-UTU</a><br />\n<br />\n活在又苦又甜的當下 <br />\n已經長大的我偶爾也會受傷失眠<br />\n<br />\n被許多人嘲笑 說是癡人夢想<br />\n但是 只要不放棄 夢想<br />\n一定有出口<br />\n<br />\nKeep on Believing 香港人<br />\n<br />\n620罷工罷課公投 期待有你參與<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sZHv9da.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsZHv9da.jpg&h=59b5f3d0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tntfATb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtntfATb.jpg&h=014d63ba&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wuQxC6x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwuQxC6x.jpg&h=c9eb48c1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w320MZT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw320MZT.jpg&h=ed8375ff&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7agtbrz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7agtbrz.jpg&h=6c264fc7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/coeeRrA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcoeeRrA.jpg&h=9b704f76&s={